 The anchor investor in the Benin Enterprise and Industrial Park would soon be moving into the facility, as the Edo State Government has finalised plans to invest the N2.1 billion that will accrue from its divestment of 50 per cent of its equity in the Edo-Azura Power Project, into the park. Continue reading Edo to invest N2.1bn Azura power proceeds in Benin industrial park at Vanguard News. Source: Vanguard